title: Honey-mustard duck breasts with butternut squash
ingredients: ['1 butternut squash', '1 or 2 tablespoons of olive oil', 'sea \u200b\u200bsalt, to taste', '1 tablespoon of crushed peppercorns', '2 tablespoons of finely chopped parsley, divided', '4 (175g) duck breast fillets', '4 tablespoons of honey', '4 tablespoons of sugar', '1 tablespoon Dijon mustard']
